{"article_id":"cIsmDddDkB8mW3Oz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Robert Mueller wants to talk to Donald Trump .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"The President wants to talk to the special counsel","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"-- so it 's a done deal right ?","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Trump appeared on Wednesday to make a significant gesture","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"by telling reporters","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that he wanted to testify to Mueller","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"-- and was ready to do so under oath .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"His offer came","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"a day after it emerged that the Mueller had requested an interview with the President","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"as he apparently begins to wind up one branch of his investigation","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"into whether Trump obstructed justice","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"by firing FBI Director James Comey","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"while he was probing alleged collusion between the Trump campaign and Russia during the 2016 election .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"`` I am looking forward to it , actually , ''","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"before offering a preview of what his testimony might look like .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"`` Here is the story :","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"There has been no collusion whatsoever .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"There is no obstruction whatsoever , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Taking a step further , on the second day in a row of blockbuster disclosures about the Mueller probe ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Trump offered to do the interview under oath .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` I would do it , ''","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"`` I would do it under oath , yeah . ''","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"On the face of it , his statement represented a significant breakthrough in the Russia investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"since earlier this month Trump questioned","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"why an interview would be needed","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"because there had been `` no collusion . ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"But the timing of the comment , the circumstances of his legal team 's ongoing negotiations with Mueller and the President 's own record","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"of reversing apparently adamant statements","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"mean it should be treated with caution .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"It was also not immediately clear","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"if Trump 's move was a coordinated strategy with his legal team ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"or a case of the President characteristically speaking off the cuff in a way","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that could give his lawyers fits .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Of course , the President , in the belief","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that he is innocent","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"and not at all threatened by the Mueller probe","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"could simply be willing to testify under oath","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"because he thinks","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"it 's the quickest way out from under the Russia cloud .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"That 's because","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"though Mueller seems to be getting to the end of the obstruction piece of the investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"it would be wrong to conclude that his tactics point to an eventual finding","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that Trump is guilty of a serious transgression .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"He could simply be working through the process of interviews and evidence","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"before wrapping up this area of inquiry ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"an interview with Trump could fast-track that process .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Even if the President knew","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"he was in some jeopardy from Mueller 's investigation ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"offering up front to testify could be a smart move","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"-- as it makes him look like he has nothing to hide , as part of the pre-interview game of expectations setting .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"given that he left himself a significant caveat ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the authenticity of his offer could be in doubt .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` I would love to do it .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"You know ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"again ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"I have to say , subject to my lawyers and all of that ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"but I would love to do it , ''","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"So","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"if he changes his mind in the future ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Trump will have benefited from the political value","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"of being seen as publicly willing to testify","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"-- but could row back","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"by saying","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"though he would love to help ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"he is bowing to the advice of his legal team","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"to respectfully decline .","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"Trump 's comments also come at a critical moment of negotiations on the format and scope of an interview between his representatives as the special counsel 's office .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"CNN 's Gloria Borger and Pamela Brown reported Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that Mueller wants to know about the President allegedly asking Comey to drop the investigation into former national security adviser Michael Flynn","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and about his reaction to Comey 's May 2017 testimony on Capitol Hill .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"He 's also interested in the President 's outreach to intelligence agencies about the Russia investigation .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"By saying","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"he 's ready to talk ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Trump could be taking part in a good cop/bad cop routine with his legal team","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"as it haggles over the terms of any interview .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Discussions could center on whether Trump will be allowed to give written answers , where or when the interview might take place","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"and if his legal representatives can be in the room .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"In true wheeler-dealer style , Trump may have simply made an opening offer on Wednesday ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"that will eventually be whittled down to more limited terms in a final deal .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"There 's also the possibility","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"however that he may have been acting impulsively ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"a plausible scenario","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"since he has a record over his first year in office","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"of supplying answers","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"that his audience at any particular time wants to hear .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"One member of Trump 's legal team , Ty Cobb , appeared to hint","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that the President 's comments were not his definitive position","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"when he said in a statement","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"that the President had been `` speaking hurriedly '' to reporters","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"before departing on a trip to Switzerland .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"`` He remains committed to continued complete cooperation with the","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"( special counsel )","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"and is looking forward to speaking with Mr. Mueller , ''","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Cobb said ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"that arrangements were being worked out between Mr. Mueller 's team and the President 's personal lawyers .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"If Trump was just shooting from the hip ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"it 's possible that he has actually weakened his legal team 's hand ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"since Mueller could now presumably , argue","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that Trump has agreed to his terms","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"so there 's no sense","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"waiting any longer","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"to get together .","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Michael Zeldin , a CNN legal analyst","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"who once worked for Mueller at the Justice Department ,","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"the President may have just put his lawyers in a difficult spot .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"`` Mueller should say to Ty Cobb and John Dowd ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"'Good , your client is all ready to go ,","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"we are all ready to go ,","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"let 's do it in the Map Room on Tuesday with a court reporter","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"and we will settle this thing . ' ''","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"that the unscripted appearance of the President","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"talking about this","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"has to make his lawyers a bit nuts","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"because it 's very hard to walk this back , ''","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"Zeldin said on AC 360 ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"adding","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"that the question","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"that would be immediately asked","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"if Trump 's lawyers advised him not to talk to Mueller ,","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"is :","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"What is he hiding ?","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"CNN has previously reported","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"that some Trump allies do not want him to testify voluntarily to Mueller ,","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"fearing","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"he could put his presidency and personal legal position in jeopardy","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"if he does so .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"And","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"given Trump 's demonstrated propensity","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"to stretch the truth ,","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"his voluble temperament and unwillingness","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"to listen to advice ,","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"some legal experts also warn","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"that an interview with Mueller could be a perjury trap .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":285,"left":0,"right":284,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":145,"right":283,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":1,"right":144,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":213,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":166,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":154,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":148,"right":153,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":146,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":8,"right":152,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":9,"right":151,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":10,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":149,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":160,"right":164,"relation":"joint","n